WEBVTT

00:01.410 --> 00:04.530
And so, this number is 
canceled out and—

00:03.900 --> 00:04.970
Teacher.

00:04.970 --> 00:08.680
In that case, wouldn't it be more 
efficient to use this formula?

00:08.940 --> 00:12.770
My, Prince Cecil. No such theorem exists.

00:12.770 --> 00:15.860
Indeed. I've just created it.

00:13.740 --> 00:15.860
<b>Cecil 10 Years Old</b>

00:15.860 --> 00:19.640
What? Your Highness is 
exceptional, but that isn't...

00:20.710 --> 00:22.410
I-It works?!

00:22.410 --> 00:25.290
But that means this is a new discovery 
in the world of mathematics!

00:25.850 --> 00:30.660
<i>By connecting the parts we were given, 
I believe it arises quite simply.</i>

00:31.430 --> 00:35.180
I-I'm going to go make 
a report to the society!

00:35.590 --> 00:37.300
<i>He's gone.</i>

00:37.660 --> 00:38.910
<i>Well, it doesn't matter.</i>

00:38.910 --> 00:41.130
<i>When I can understand a thing 
after hearing it once,</i>

00:41.130 --> 00:44.090
<i>I can't say that hearing it over a 
prolonged period of time is beneficial.</i>

00:44.590 --> 00:47.080
<i>Oh, how boring.</i>

00:49.730 --> 00:51.120
Prince Cecil!

00:55.200 --> 00:57.610
I am a villainess!

00:57.610 --> 01:01.080
My role is to rip Your Highness and 
the heroine away from each other,

01:01.080 --> 01:04.190
and have you left in
complete shock in the end!

01:04.940 --> 01:08.100
<i>Yes, that makes no sense at all.</i>

01:25.770 --> 01:27.060
<b>An Observation Log of My
 Fiancée Who Calls Herself a Villainess</b>

02:39.010 --> 02:42.010
<b>Chapter 1</b>

02:39.010 --> 02:42.010
<b>An Observation Log of Meeting a
 Self-Proclaimed Villainess.</b>

02:46.030 --> 02:49.150
<i>I am Cecil Glo Alphasta.</i>

02:50.290 --> 02:54.500
<i>I am the First Prince of the Kingdom 
of Alphasta and its crown prince.</i>

02:56.130 --> 02:58.410
<i>Today is the day that my fiancée,</i>

02:58.410 --> 03:01.590
<i>Bertia Ibil Noches, daughter of a marquis,</i>

03:01.590 --> 03:03.910
<i>and I first met face-to-face. However...</i>

03:04.230 --> 03:09.530
<i>it seems that I'm not the only one who 
doesn't understand what she's saying.</i>

03:11.820 --> 03:14.830
Miss Bertia, standing and chatting 
isn't really the thing to do.

03:14.830 --> 03:16.920
Would you like to have
some tea while we talk?

03:16.920 --> 03:18.090
What?

03:18.090 --> 03:19.620
Y-Yes.

03:24.750 --> 03:26.400
This is Zeno.

03:25.760 --> 03:29.390
<b>Zeno</b>

03:26.400 --> 03:29.390
He's my personal butler. 
Please look on him kindly.

03:29.390 --> 03:31.640
Stare...

03:32.440 --> 03:33.650
Is something wrong?

03:33.650 --> 03:38.310
Prince Cecil, aren't you a little 
too composed for your age?

03:39.130 --> 03:41.360
Is it possible that 
you're a reincarnation?

03:41.750 --> 03:43.370
<i>A reincarnation?</i>

03:43.850 --> 03:48.210
I was taught that this is how
royals should behave themselves.

03:48.210 --> 03:49.280
It's only natural.

03:49.280 --> 03:51.220
<i>No, it isn't!</i>

03:51.220 --> 03:52.360
<i>If there was some other detached,</i>

03:52.360 --> 03:54.420
<i>philosophical, ten-year-old prince,
 no one could stand it!</i>

03:54.420 --> 03:57.040
<i>The voice inside your heart 
is spilling out, Zeno.</i>

03:57.390 --> 04:00.880
Well, then. Will you explain 
what you were saying before?

04:01.840 --> 04:03.580
Of course!

04:03.580 --> 04:06.210
I must have Your Highness 
understand everything

04:06.210 --> 04:09.600
and become a person worthy of spurning me.

04:09.990 --> 04:15.110
This may shock you, but I have 
memories of my past life.

04:15.400 --> 04:17.890
In the land where I was 
born and raised, Japan,

04:17.890 --> 04:21.600
there were stories I could watch with 
moving pictures that were like novels.

04:20.400 --> 04:21.860
Japan
 Woman A Playing a Game

04:21.860 --> 04:27.740
Cecil Glo Alphasta

04:22.060 --> 04:25.920
These "otome games" were 
something I enjoyed immensely.

04:25.920 --> 04:27.740
Hey, it's you.

04:26.160 --> 04:27.740
<b>"Hey, it's you."</b>

04:28.060 --> 04:30.750
Then, when I regained my memories,

04:31.020 --> 04:32.370
that's when I realized..

04:32.370 --> 04:36.470
That otome game had depicted this world.

04:37.240 --> 04:41.140
That's why I know the whole 
scenario... the future.

04:41.140 --> 04:45.890
Your Highness will fall in love with a
noble's daughter, the Maiden of Destiny.

04:46.130 --> 04:51.390
I, the villainess, will turn into a 
jealous demon and torment her horribly.

04:51.390 --> 04:53.270
This will enrage Your Highness.

04:53.270 --> 04:56.640
You'll break off our engagement,
and my house will fall into ruin!

04:56.640 --> 05:01.950
In short, getting the better of me allows 
the two of you to find happiness together!

05:01.950 --> 05:05.140
Though my fate is to fall, 
I will do it beautifully!

05:05.140 --> 05:08.650
I will become a first-rate flower of evil!

05:09.240 --> 05:14.800
<i>Before this, I've never once been unable 
to understand what someone was saying.</i>

05:15.090 --> 05:18.640
<i>Though, to be honest, whether she 
has an overactive imagination,</i>

05:18.640 --> 05:21.930
<i>or the power to predict the 
future, it doesn't matter to me.</i>

05:22.230 --> 05:26.720
<i>In short, she's aiming to become a person 
who fits into this scenario of hers.</i>

05:26.720 --> 05:30.870
<i>As long as it isn't something problematic 
for a future queen, I don't mind at all.</i>

05:31.300 --> 05:36.310
I was wondering, what exactly is this
first-rate flower of evil you mentioned?

05:36.310 --> 05:38.650
Strong, noble, and beautiful!

05:38.650 --> 05:42.440
Though her path may lead to destruction, 
she treads it without hesitation!

05:42.440 --> 05:44.150
That's the kind of
woman I'm talking about!

05:44.550 --> 05:46.900
Strong, noble...

05:46.900 --> 05:48.410
and beautiful?

05:50.160 --> 05:52.360
<i>Oh, I slipped!</i>

05:56.150 --> 05:58.190
N-No, you have the wrong idea!

05:58.190 --> 06:01.180
Bertia was always supposed to be someone 
who didn't really have a chance.

06:01.180 --> 06:03.500
So, as a character,
 her appearance is questionable.

06:03.790 --> 06:06.490
She sounds like a sad sort of person.

06:06.490 --> 06:08.390
Are you all right with all of that?

06:08.790 --> 06:10.750
I am not all right.

06:10.750 --> 06:13.280
Everything I spoke of was 
the Bertia in the game.

06:13.780 --> 06:17.370
I am... I am myself!

06:17.990 --> 06:21.990
In my past life, I tended to hide in 
my own shell, but you were my support.

06:21.990 --> 06:25.370
Prince Cecil, I wish for your happiness!

06:26.010 --> 06:31.270
And that is why I will become an 
honest, righteous flower of evil!

06:31.570 --> 06:34.370
<i>An honest, righteous flower of evil?</i>

06:35.140 --> 06:38.250
I will improve myself and come again!

06:38.480 --> 06:39.830
A pleasant day to you!

06:39.870 --> 06:41.620
Bertia has run away

06:42.040 --> 06:43.680
I wonder what all that was.

06:44.130 --> 06:46.570
Your Highness, what will you do?

06:48.130 --> 06:49.830
Well...

06:49.830 --> 06:51.860
as far as becoming my fiancée,

06:51.860 --> 06:54.940
she has none of the manners necessary 
to interact with royalty,

06:54.940 --> 06:57.260
and I don't understand many
of her words and actions.

06:57.260 --> 06:59.800
And that is exactly what 
makes her so entertaining.

06:59.800 --> 07:01.710
I will observe her for a while.

07:01.710 --> 07:03.870
If it becomes necessary, 
I need only tame—

07:03.870 --> 07:07.020
lead her down the correct path.

07:07.310 --> 07:09.330
You seem like you're enjoying yourself.

07:09.330 --> 07:12.820
This sense of unpredictability 
isn't bad at all.

07:12.820 --> 07:17.510
<i>Generally, if I try something, 
I can do it on my first attempt,</i>

07:17.510 --> 07:19.830
<i>so, for me, the world is a tedious place.</i>

07:20.130 --> 07:23.760
<i>I've rarely ever felt a 
sense of accomplishment.</i>

07:23.760 --> 07:26.780
<i>In my eyes, the world has lost its color.</i>

07:28.130 --> 07:29.340
<i>Which is why...</i>

07:33.580 --> 07:36.100
<i>I hope you won't betray my expectations.</i>

07:37.470 --> 07:39.930
One Year Later

07:43.930 --> 07:47.570
Your Highness, there is a 
report from that messenger.

07:50.570 --> 07:53.900
Lady Bertia has secluded herself 
within her home for a year.

07:53.900 --> 07:55.820
Surely it's cause for concern now.

07:55.820 --> 07:59.570
I've been sending messengers 
to go and see how she's faring.

07:59.570 --> 08:01.950
She's in exceedingly good spirits.

08:01.950 --> 08:05.090
Then why has she shut herself away?

08:05.090 --> 08:07.280
Zeno, you will understand 
once you see her.

08:07.280 --> 08:09.640
She should make an appearance very soon.

08:10.550 --> 08:12.630
A Few Days Later

08:14.790 --> 08:16.760
It has been quite some 
time, Your Highness.

08:17.030 --> 08:19.770
You don't know who I am, you say?

08:21.500 --> 08:23.940
Bertia Ibil Noches!

08:23.940 --> 08:26.030
Your Highness's fiancée!

08:26.030 --> 08:29.850
<i>Well, this is something. Her 
appearance has changed quite a bit.</i>

08:30.250 --> 08:32.360
<i>It seems that those reports were true.</i>

08:32.360 --> 08:34.570
Just two more kilos!

08:34.570 --> 08:37.320
Did you mistake me for someone else? 
You didn't recognize me, did you?

08:37.320 --> 08:38.490
Ow!

08:37.320 --> 08:37.490
<b>THUMP</b>

08:37.490 --> 08:37.740
<b>THUMP</b>

08:37.740 --> 08:38.450
<b>THUMP</b>

08:38.490 --> 08:41.490
What sort of attitude is that to take 
toward the crown prince, Bertia?

08:41.490 --> 08:43.670
What are you doing, Father?

08:43.670 --> 08:46.800
Your Highness, please forgive 
my idiot daughter's rudeness.

08:46.800 --> 08:48.540
Please, don't let it trouble you.

08:48.540 --> 08:50.920
It's quite childlike and 
adorable, wouldn't you say?

08:52.790 --> 08:58.770
Y-Your Highness... would you 
please say that one more time?

08:59.240 --> 09:02.380
When you, um... said "adorable."

09:04.190 --> 09:05.560
Bertia.

09:06.450 --> 09:10.190
Don't let his appearance fool you. His 
Highness's eyes never smile, do they?

09:10.190 --> 09:14.020
He doesn't have the emotions necessary
to dote on cute things. He's too cold.

09:14.020 --> 09:17.540
You will make do with my 
love-filled use of "adorable."

09:17.900 --> 09:19.780
You're adorable!

09:19.780 --> 09:25.540
<i>I wonder if the marquis is aware that 
what he said was ruder than Miss Bertia.</i>

09:32.140 --> 09:33.750
Oh, Kuro!

09:35.210 --> 09:37.490
I knew it. It is alive, isn't it?

09:37.490 --> 09:39.130
I'm terribly sorry.

09:39.130 --> 09:42.110
Ever since I took her in, 
she won't leave my side.

09:42.110 --> 09:44.890
So I had her imitate a scarf 
and brought her with me.

09:44.890 --> 09:46.350
<i>Imitate.</i>

09:46.350 --> 09:50.190
<i>It wasn't a successful imitation, 
but still, this is...</i>

09:52.140 --> 09:54.320
<i>I thought it must be so.</i>

09:54.320 --> 09:58.150
<i>If I keep quiet about it now, it'll make
 things more entertaining in the future.</i>

09:58.150 --> 10:01.810
Now, please have some sweets 
before the tea gets cold.

10:01.810 --> 10:03.660
Thank you! I'll have some!

10:05.330 --> 10:06.860
Diet.

10:07.170 --> 10:09.750
This cake was made with a 
reduced amount of sugar.

10:09.750 --> 10:12.460
I'm not particularly good 
with sweets, you see?

10:12.460 --> 10:15.010
Reduced sugar! Cake!

10:15.010 --> 10:16.830
Please, have some.

10:21.610 --> 10:25.840
<i>I thought she was aiming to become a 
strong, noble flower of evil, wasn't she?</i>

10:26.180 --> 10:29.750
<i>I feel like she's heading in 
the opposite direction.</i>

10:29.750 --> 10:32.850
Well, shall we begin speaking of tomorrow?

10:32.850 --> 10:35.420
Yes! At the party tomorrow,
as a first-rate villainess,

10:35.420 --> 10:40.360
I'll nobly fulfill my duty as
Your Highness's partner!

10:40.710 --> 10:42.150
<i>Why is it, I wonder?</i>

10:42.150 --> 10:45.000
<i>She meant to seem reliable, 
but now I feel anxious.</i>

10:45.000 --> 10:47.190
That's very reassuring.

10:47.190 --> 10:50.880
But the fact that you're a villainess and 
that you have memories of a past life...

10:50.880 --> 10:53.240
let's keep that a secret 
between just you and I.

10:53.240 --> 10:54.760
Why?

10:54.760 --> 10:57.930
Because the high society that 
we're about to enter into

10:57.930 --> 11:01.010
is a world where you never know what 
may end up having a harmful result.

11:03.890 --> 11:07.980
A flower of evil who leaves herself open 
to attack would seem inferior, no?

11:07.980 --> 11:09.760
I-I see!

11:09.760 --> 11:12.420
Defeating one's opponents 
in secret is first-rate,

11:12.420 --> 11:14.950
while talking big and 
digging one's own grave is third-rate!

11:14.950 --> 11:16.320
I completely understand!

11:16.320 --> 11:18.550
I'm different from the Bertia in the game

11:18.550 --> 11:21.400
because I will become a beautiful, 
noble flower of evil!

11:21.400 --> 11:23.640
I'm so glad you understand.

11:23.640 --> 11:26.030
<i>Though I feel her understanding 
is slightly skewed.</i>

11:26.030 --> 11:31.430
Tomorrow is my eleventh birthday, and I'm
happy to have you there celebrating it.

11:31.430 --> 11:34.850
I'm also happy that I will be 
celebrating Your Highness's...

11:36.830 --> 11:38.220
Eleven?

11:38.220 --> 11:40.540
Your Highness is turning eleven years old?

11:40.540 --> 11:42.800
That's right. You didn't know?

11:44.420 --> 11:48.710
No, I knew. It's just...

11:48.710 --> 11:52.290
Which means that on my next 
birthday, I'll turn ten.

11:53.700 --> 11:58.890
Your Highness, my mother... 
my mother is going to die!

11:59.250 --> 12:01.270
Your mother?

12:01.590 --> 12:03.080
According to the scenario,

12:03.080 --> 12:05.660
it will be from an epidemic that 
starts spreading in the summer.

12:05.940 --> 12:11.280
Just before my tenth birthday, 
my mother will die.

12:11.640 --> 12:13.160
An epidemic?

12:13.160 --> 12:16.250
Apparently, a certain 
infectious disease evolves.

12:16.250 --> 12:19.270
It takes time to find a method 
to treat it, and on top of that,

12:19.270 --> 12:21.300
the herb needed for the medicine...

12:21.300 --> 12:23.370
luona leaf, there won't be enough of it.

12:23.370 --> 12:26.180
A great many people will lose their lives.

12:26.510 --> 12:28.130
<i>Luona leaf.</i>

12:28.130 --> 12:31.420
<i>It's definitely a medicinal 
plant that is difficult to cultivate.</i>

12:31.720 --> 12:36.110
Father searches frantically for luona 
leaf, but he isn't able to obtain any.

12:36.520 --> 12:41.240
In the end, he asks His Majesty
to spare him some, but...

12:52.990 --> 12:56.410
What you're speaking of happens 
a year from now, doesn't it?

12:56.410 --> 12:59.210
If you prepare for it now, won't 
you be able to save your mother?

12:59.500 --> 13:01.960
But, if I do that, the scenario will...

13:01.960 --> 13:05.390
The scenario or your mother? 
Which is more important?

13:05.390 --> 13:07.260
Of course my mother is!

13:07.790 --> 13:12.460
But... but if the scenario gets 
twisted, Your Highness will...

13:12.910 --> 13:14.190
<i>Me?</i>

13:14.950 --> 13:15.890
Your Highness.

13:16.770 --> 13:19.100
Here. Wipe your tears.

13:19.100 --> 13:21.290
I'm your fiancé.

13:21.670 --> 13:25.480
If you ever find yourself in trouble, 
let's think about what to do together.

13:30.660 --> 13:32.370
<b>One Year Later</b>

13:30.660 --> 13:32.370
Noches House

13:32.360 --> 13:34.240
Your Highness is simply awful!

13:35.630 --> 13:40.250
Honestly! Honestly! Oh, 
honestly, honestly, honestly!

13:41.760 --> 13:46.100
P-Please, forgive me. That behavior 
was unbecoming of a lady.

13:46.100 --> 13:48.390
No, I should be the one to apologize.

13:48.390 --> 13:52.680
Have I done something to cause that 
charming face of yours to crumple?

13:52.680 --> 13:56.160
Today is already my tenth birthday!

13:56.160 --> 13:59.360
I wanted to develop more of a 
strategy against the epidemic...

13:59.360 --> 14:03.290
but in your letters you only 
ever replied, "It's all right."

14:03.290 --> 14:05.150
What was I supposed to do?

14:07.900 --> 14:09.190
I'm sorry.

14:09.190 --> 14:12.520
I didn't realize that you 
were feeling so distraught.

14:12.520 --> 14:16.350
But everything really is all right. 
That's why I wrote that in my letters.

14:16.350 --> 14:20.410
I desperately tried to collect luona 
leaf, but I don't have nearly enough.

14:20.630 --> 14:23.610
And for some reason, when summer 
came, the disease didn't spread.

14:23.610 --> 14:25.430
And my mother is in perfect health.

14:25.430 --> 14:29.050
I just don't understand 
what's going on anymore!

14:29.280 --> 14:33.580
Don't worry. The epidemic did 
begin, just as you said it would.

14:33.580 --> 14:35.810
It's simply already died down.

14:36.230 --> 14:38.560
So the infectious disease 
really did spread?

14:38.870 --> 14:40.010
What?

14:40.010 --> 14:44.290
I used your information to guess the 
disease and made medicine for it.

14:44.290 --> 14:47.950
As soon as it began to spread, the 
patients received immediate treatment.

14:49.940 --> 14:50.730
Huh?

14:51.730 --> 14:53.330
What?!

14:53.330 --> 14:56.710
W-Wait, Your Highness! What do you mean?

14:56.710 --> 15:00.090
<i>You're the only one allowed to 
treat me this way, Miss Bertia.</i>

15:00.090 --> 15:02.470
I understand. First, 
let's calm down a little.

15:02.470 --> 15:05.970
How can I possibly stay calm? 
Hurry up and explain, please!

15:05.970 --> 15:07.830
Let's take a little walk outside.

15:11.100 --> 15:15.630
Now, let's go back to just after 
you spoke to me about your mother.

15:17.880 --> 15:20.760
His Majesty seemed to be very pleased.

15:19.730 --> 15:28.190
<b>One Year Ago</b>

15:19.730 --> 15:28.190
The Royal Palace

15:20.760 --> 15:23.690
He gave you permission to use 
the greenhouse right away.

15:23.690 --> 15:26.770
Perhaps, with the worry of what to get 
his son as a birthday present gone,

15:26.770 --> 15:28.190
he felt relieved.

15:28.190 --> 15:30.150
And what will you do next?

15:30.150 --> 15:31.860
First, the library.

15:31.860 --> 15:34.160
I must look into luona leaf.

15:42.370 --> 15:44.420
Some Time Later

15:46.420 --> 15:49.710
<i>It was so simple to successfully 
cultivate luona leaf.</i>

15:46.420 --> 15:53.550
<b>A giant luona plant has grown.</b>

15:49.710 --> 15:53.540
Luona leaf grows this big? Was 
it Your Highness who grew this?

15:53.540 --> 15:56.520
<i>Since I have this, maybe I'll 
try making some medicine.</i>

15:54.590 --> 15:56.520
This is the discovery of the century!

15:56.520 --> 15:59.300
<i>To do that, I'll first have to 
identify the infectious disease.</i>

15:56.520 --> 15:57.920
It's magnificent!

15:59.670 --> 16:02.420
<i>I asked Miss Bertia about the 
characteristics of the disease...</i>

16:00.270 --> 16:04.560
<b>Asked Questions at Noches House</b>

16:02.420 --> 16:04.570
My mother's disease?

16:04.570 --> 16:07.530
<i>I borrowed knowledge from experts 
in medicine and pharmacy...</i>

16:05.150 --> 16:12.950
<b>Asked Questions at the Royal Palace</b>

16:07.530 --> 16:09.670
<i>and I was able to identify the disease.</i>

16:09.670 --> 16:12.950
There's nothing left that I 
can teach you, Your Highness.

16:13.370 --> 16:16.700
<i>It's likely that the disease 
is a mutation of this one.</i>

16:13.450 --> 16:16.700
Read a Mountain of Books.

16:17.030 --> 16:18.950
<i>And so a remedy...</i>

16:17.120 --> 16:18.950
Performed a Number of Experiments

16:19.410 --> 16:22.080
Easily Completed.

16:19.800 --> 16:21.410
<i>I've gone and done it.</i>

16:22.080 --> 16:24.470
You made it quite easily, didn't you?

16:24.470 --> 16:26.530
Well, we don't know if 
it's effective or not.

16:26.530 --> 16:30.090
There's no way to test it without 
someone stricken by the disease.

16:30.350 --> 16:35.740
<i>But if we truly want to be prepared, I'll 
have to make the adults take action.</i>

16:36.420 --> 16:40.760
<i>I'll pretend that I just happened to 
take an interest in a certain disease,</i>

16:40.760 --> 16:44.190
<i>and invite a doctor who is studying 
it to the palace as my teacher.</i>

16:44.190 --> 16:47.210
<i>I'll passionately discuss 
infectious diseases.</i>

16:47.210 --> 16:48.520
I vehemently insist!

16:48.520 --> 16:52.830
<i>Then we'll discuss the possibility of a 
new strain and how to combat it.</i>

16:52.830 --> 16:54.270
I vehemently insist!

16:54.270 --> 16:55.550
<i>As a separate matter,</i>

16:55.550 --> 16:59.560
<i>I'll tell him about the effects of the
luona leaf I happen to be obsessed with,</i>

16:59.300 --> 17:00.700
A huge hint!

16:59.560 --> 17:01.040
<i>and speak quite passionately.</i>

17:00.120 --> 17:01.030
Cecil provided him with a big hint.

17:01.270 --> 17:04.640
<i>Then, I set it up so that the new disease 
strain would connect to the luona leaf.</i>

17:04.640 --> 17:07.390
<i>If I can get him to come to the 
realization himself, then...</i>

17:07.390 --> 17:09.380
If it has such effects,

17:09.380 --> 17:12.040
then it's likely to be useful in my 
colleague's research...

17:12.040 --> 17:13.540
I'll tell them about it.

17:13.130 --> 17:17.680
The effect was lackluster.

17:13.540 --> 17:17.670
<i>It's not in your colleague's research,
but yours that it should prove useful.</i>

17:20.430 --> 17:23.540
<i>Why is he unable to realize 
something so simple?</i>

17:23.540 --> 17:26.170
Your Highness, you seem to be 
fighting a difficult battle.

17:26.170 --> 17:28.730
And you seem oddly happy, Zeno.

17:28.730 --> 17:30.060
No, not especially.

17:30.300 --> 17:32.880
<i>Still, he is an excellent doctor.</i>

17:32.880 --> 17:35.070
<i>I'm sure he'll realize eventually.</i>

17:35.570 --> 17:37.570
<b>A Few Months Later</b>

17:37.570 --> 17:38.980
I vehemently insist!

17:38.980 --> 17:40.370
I vehemently insist!

17:40.720 --> 17:42.870
Could it be...

17:42.870 --> 17:46.600
wouldn't that luona leaf have 
some effect against the disease?

17:43.330 --> 17:50.750
The doctors had a revelation.

17:46.600 --> 17:48.590
Perhaps it would.

17:48.590 --> 17:50.750
<i>That took a long time.</i>

17:51.280 --> 17:53.040
That's how it happened.

17:53.040 --> 17:56.200
After some time, the first patient 
with the disease was discovered,

17:56.200 --> 17:58.760
and that same doctor gave her 
thorough medical treatment.

17:59.160 --> 18:03.060
<i>The truth is that when a patient 
really did appear, I was surprised.</i>

18:03.060 --> 18:07.000
<i>Because it wasn't as if I completely 
believed Miss Bertia's story.</i>

18:07.510 --> 18:11.000
<i>But I learned a lot.</i>

18:11.000 --> 18:13.680
<i>The fact that I had difficulty 
guiding the doctor...</i>

18:13.680 --> 18:16.700
<i>and the fact that I made Miss 
Bertia feel so anxious...</i>

18:16.700 --> 18:19.030
<i>might be the result of my bad habits.</i>

18:19.270 --> 18:21.660
<i>When I theorize, I understand too easily.</i>

18:21.660 --> 18:24.620
<i>And I seem to have a tendency 
to omit explanations.</i>

18:24.620 --> 18:26.840
J-Just a moment, please.

18:26.840 --> 18:28.670
So much of that seems strange.

18:28.670 --> 18:30.720
Your Highness, why would 
you do all of that?

18:30.720 --> 18:32.470
Why?

18:32.470 --> 18:36.590
I have no intention of ignoring my 
fiancée when she appears so anxious.

18:36.590 --> 18:40.970
B-But an eleven year old child 
could hardly do all of that!

18:40.970 --> 18:43.120
I am the crown prince.

18:43.120 --> 18:44.970
I can use the palace library,

18:44.970 --> 18:46.570
and with my father's permission,

18:46.570 --> 18:50.050
it's possible for me to call 
on brilliant experts for help.

18:50.050 --> 18:52.360
R-Really?

18:52.360 --> 18:53.880
<i>No, of course not!</i>

18:53.880 --> 18:56.170
<i>For a normal crown prince,
it would be impossible!</i>

18:56.170 --> 18:57.360
<i>That's amazing, Zeno!</i>

18:57.360 --> 19:00.280
<i>You're so far away, and yet I can 
hear the voice of your heart.</i>

19:00.280 --> 19:03.150
Is it really possible for things 
to work out so conveniently?

19:03.150 --> 19:06.430
I suppose I should expect it from the 
genius known as the Android Prince.

19:06.430 --> 19:07.810
<i>Android?</i>

19:08.160 --> 19:10.870
Please don't worry about the details.

19:10.870 --> 19:14.730
If your mother is safe and the harm 
to the people was kept to a minimum,

19:14.730 --> 19:16.000
then everything's fine, isn't it?

19:16.000 --> 19:18.180
Y-Yes, you're right!

19:18.180 --> 19:21.070
After all, everyone has evaded the 
evil clutches of the epidemic.

19:21.070 --> 19:22.470
This is for the best!

19:22.470 --> 19:25.340
<i>Yes. I see you've given 
up on thinking about it.</i>

19:25.600 --> 19:28.490
Oh, that's right. Aside 
from the official gift,

19:28.490 --> 19:30.600
I have something else I'd like 
to give you, Miss Bertia.

19:30.600 --> 19:32.820
You still have some 
other surprise for me?!

19:32.820 --> 19:37.000
It's from me personally.
A handmade birthday present.

19:38.180 --> 19:41.710
Oh, it's lovely!

19:41.710 --> 19:44.860
The truth is that this is 
actually a universal antidote.

19:44.860 --> 19:46.440
Wh-What?

19:46.440 --> 19:49.330
A universal antidote?

19:49.330 --> 19:51.550
While I was researching 
all sorts of things,

19:51.550 --> 19:54.590
I found an interesting book 
in the palace library.

19:55.970 --> 19:57.150
What's that?

20:00.950 --> 20:02.200
A seam?

20:03.710 --> 20:05.050
It moved.

20:15.880 --> 20:18.810
Using the knowledge I gained 
from there, I tried making that.

20:18.810 --> 20:23.880
Since you'll become my wife, it's possible
 that your life will be threatened.

20:23.880 --> 20:25.820
I thought it could be a protective charm.

20:28.000 --> 20:30.450
Yes, it suits you very well.

20:38.210 --> 20:41.470
Th-Thank you... very much.

20:45.540 --> 20:46.960
Prince Cecil.

20:47.890 --> 20:53.160
I, Bertia Ibil Noches, 
swear upon this necklace!

20:53.730 --> 20:56.150
In order to repay the debt 
of gratitude I owe you,

20:56.150 --> 20:58.520
I will make sure to thoroughly 
rectify the scenario...

20:58.520 --> 21:01.130
and I will show you what a magnificent 
villainess I can become!

21:04.460 --> 21:07.430
First, my father, who should have 
started down the path of evil...

21:07.430 --> 21:09.680
I'll have him turn into a proper villain!

21:09.680 --> 21:11.340
No, that's really all right.

21:11.340 --> 21:13.510
Losing a chancellor would
cause problems, after all.

21:13.510 --> 21:16.630
I will make sure that Your Highness 
and the heroine get your happy ending!

21:16.990 --> 21:21.090
<i>Yes. It seems she isn't listening 
to most of what I'm saying.</i>

21:21.380 --> 21:24.200
<i>Well, that's all right. It does 
seem entertaining, after all.</i>

21:24.200 --> 21:26.370
I'll give it my very best!

21:25.880 --> 21:27.970
<b>Bertia has renewed her resolution.</b>

21:28.220 --> 21:34.060
<b>Translator:
Timer:
Editor:
Quality Control:
Final Quality Control:</b>

21:28.220 --> 21:34.060
