Edgar Cruz
Salem Alabanza
Alicia Ashby
Michelle Tymon</b>

23:07.090 --> 23:09.290
Are you injured?

23:16.030 --> 23:19.190
It's all right. There's 
nothing to be scared of.

23:29.570 --> 23:31.350
I remember...

23:32.240 --> 23:33.940
I am...

23:34.970 --> 23:40.050
<b>Chapter 2














An Observation Log of the Self-Proclaimed
 Villainess's Debut into Society.</b>

